cruft-utils (2.0-1) stable

  * Remove custom configuration.
  * Add configuration directory "/usr/lib/cruft-utils".
  * Add manpages.

  [ General Cruft ]

  * Present checksums of configuration files.
  * Changed package files can be filtered via "/usr/lib/cruft-utils/changes-filter".
  * Changed package files can be filtered via "/usr/lib/cruft-utils/config-filter".

  [ Homedir Cruft ]

  * Add parameter for maximum age of files in days.



